            "id": 72725,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Inside the code block, stop the loop after running its code block by updating <code>keepPlaying</code> to <code>false</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (keepPlaying === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Yummy&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"103\" /><option startIndex=\"104\" endIndex=\"105\" /><option startIndex=\"106\" endIndex=\"111\" /><option startIndex=\"111\" endIndex=\"112\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Yummy\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>keepPlaying</code> followed by <code>=</code> and then <code>false</code>, <code>;</code>.</p></body></html>"
